{"tid":1516793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭之路上 我們都累了","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:10:21.000Z","uid":85630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2c65a4a49d078f8f63e7319bfa5c1502cc971b","tid":1516793,"uid":85630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"兩個幾月嘅抗爭，好多香港人都攰了<br />\n無論係勇武定和理非定鍵戰嘅你地<br />\n喺不斷同呢個腐敗政府鬥爭嘅時候一定會產生唔少負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得唔好將呢啲負能量放落另一半身上<br />\n你嘅另一半可以同你分擔，可以同你一齊行呢條漫漫長路 <br />\n但佢冇義務忍受你嘅冷淡或者被你將仇警情緒投射落佢地身上架<br />\n大家記得抗爭嘅同時都要好好關心另一半呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">九月一號下午一點機場見</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef977c2f5a976c8ee89800be7150d4f155e4747e","tid":1516793,"uid":85630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90239c0cb79b4daf623a7d378f21327dfc98e022","tid":1516793,"uid":85630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1號一齊入機場</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"67fe000b93ac0310529a38321a7455a829bc92e6","tid":1516793,"uid":85630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月1號一齊入機場</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0f8d7d660a54866b99e4c5e41fd32b924c91c33c","tid":1516793,"uid":85630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月1號一齊入機場</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"58c0def6d6b137d6e185e2fc84625a6068b0056f","tid":1516793,"uid"